short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: BrightSpace Open Content In A New Tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds a new-tab-button to every frame in Content, where the source can be opened in a new tab.

Open Source:
https://github.com/jespervdz/BrightSpace-Open-In-A-New-Tab-Chrome-Extension


V1.2: New manifest needed to work with new iframe source
V1.1: Use of Brightspace's API to get the file
V1.0: Initial release
